main

Class Queen

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Queen
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Ant

    public class Queen
extends java.lang.Object
implements Ant
    Every simulation begins with one Queen ant, and no more can be bought. The Queen digs down to a depth of 70 tiles and creates a nest. From then on, it is motionless, and other ants spawn around it when they are bought.
